    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Create, manage, and deliver <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-500">structured content</span>
